{
  "stem": "24212.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Because we tried to tell about a book we remember, just sort of entertain each other, to, to, to talk about sane things in-- in life.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Because we were living through insanity.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And this cooking group would cook and would say, well, take two eggs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "No, the others said, you must take three.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "There was big fight.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Two eggs or three eggs, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "No eggs in sight of course.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And they would make the dumplings, finally.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "In about 10 minutes they made the dumpling.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Then they would serve the dumplings and describe the plate and the pattern of the plate and this fork is a little bit bent, and-- But the dumplings, the Czech national dish, the dumpling.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Fruit dumplings.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And the butter, and how the rivulets of the butter flowed down the side.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And whoops, here, that-- that one drop of butter, got stuck.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "But the next one came and pushed it down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the rest of us were sitting there, you know, our mouths watering because we were constantly hungry, of course.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But this cooking business, it's not special to, to my experience.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That went on everywhere, even among the men.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were also quote unquote, 'cooking,' everyone, everybody.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It-- looking back, now that I've survived, you know, everything is very interesting.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The story I wanted to tell, and I'll try to make it very short, about what life is all about.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "After the war, I went back to this little town-- not little, just town-- where I used to go to a-- the milk bar would be the closest in, in English concept.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were selling yogurt or milk and some sweets, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I had my sweet, and then I had my yogurt.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
